snippet.title: Strange Terror From The Deep: Developer Commentary
snippet.description:
Warning: This video contains spoilers of the game, (cause obviously the game isn't out yet till January) so if you want to experience the game yourself without knowing certain things that happen in the game, don't watch it. Also, it contains some language, obviously you know that by now since this isn't a PG channel.

Anyway, I thought it'd give yall something special before Christmas, like a gameplay vid of Strange Terror From The Deep with some commentary from me, the dev. Hope you enjoy!

Wanna support me somehow? Here's my Patreon! ►https://www.patreon.com/DaveMicrowavesGames?alert=2
